# Rust build artifacts
/target
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock.orig

# The gate ledger (.mpd/state/) and config (.mpd/config.json) are intentionally
# tracked — they are the durable gate record. But the current-change pointer is
# per-developer transient state, so it is ignored (and, being untracked, cannot
# be used as a shared path-traversal vector).
.mpd/current
.mpd/tmp/

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
*.swp

# Secrets (defense in depth; mpd also blocks these at commit)
.env
*.p8
*.pem
